title: Looking for a plat jungle/top main for teams
body:
Hi :)

My team is looking for a friendly top/jungle main . We will be playing in tournaments regularly and organising scrims. Let me know if you're interested!

replies.body: Hi I'm plat 5 currently, with my peak being plat 2. I consider myself higher skill level than plat 5. I main jungle: shaco, kha'zix, fiddlesticks(actually + win-rate and great at fiddlesticks) (mid fizz secondary).
